Scott Thompson Baker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scott_Thompson_Baker 0 Scott Thompson Baker (born September 15, 1960) is an American television actor, from Golden Valley, Minnesota. Some of his most notable roles are Colton Shore on General Hospital, Craig Lawson on All My Children, and Connor Davis on The Bold and the Beautiful.
